<A>__{the bellman moves away. vivian walks to the front desk.}
<C>__{vivian}
<D>__{hi, barney!}
<C>__{mr. thomas}
<P>__{(looking up)}
<D>__{miss vivian.}
<C>__{vivian}
<D>__{look i just wanted to say goodbye.}
