<D>__{you're not accompanying him to new york?}
<C>__{vivian}
<P>__{(lightly)}
<D>__{come on, barney, you and me live in the real world.}
<P>__{(a beat)}
<D>__{you don't know how to treat a girl like anything but a lady, mr. thomas.}
<C>__{mr. thomas}
<D>__{certain ladies make that very easy... vivian.}
<P>__{(turning to the desk clerk)}
<D>__{john, call a limousine for our guest, please. have it take her anywhere she wishes to go. bill the hotel.}
